Class DFBase

java.lang.Object
  com.amlibtech.data_fields.DFBase
Direct Known Subclasses:
DFBigDecimal, DFBoolean, DFColor, DFCountry_Abbr, DFDate, DFDay_Of_Week_Numeric, DFDouble, DFFile, DFHour_Minute, DFInteger, DFInteger_Enumerated, DFMoney, DFState_Abbr, DFString, DFString_Choice_List, DFString_Encrypted_Hex, DFString_Encrypted_OBSOLETE, DFString_Enumerated, DFString_Scrambled, DFString_Var_Enumerated, DFTimestamp, DFTimeZone
public abstract class DFBase
extends java.lang.Object

This is the Base class for all DF Datafields. Data Fields contain additional information to deal with SQL databases and HTML forms. It does NOT hold a value! It should not be implimented! It does contain values to be used in ALL other DF Classes.
